    <scopecontent>
      <head>Scope and Content Information</head>
      <p>Office Administrative files of the secretary of the Board,
         including : Admissions 1972-1979, Athletics 1967-1975,
         Bayly-Tiffany Scholorships1968-1971, Conflict of Interest
         1981-1982, Development Council 1972, Dormitory Counseling
         1970, Excerpts About Minutes 1945-1966, Faculty Mortgages
         1969, Hospital 1971-1979, Legal Advisor 1970-1973, memoranda
         to Board of Visitors, 1981 Nov-1982 May, and Minutes and
         Excerpts from Correspondence, 1982.</p>
      <p>Also newspaper articles 1982, the Rotch Report (on the
         University Environment relating to the enrollment of black
         students)1969-1970, 1976, School of Medicine 1970-1978;
         1980-1981, Self-Study 1962; 1972-1973; 1975, Staff Assistance
         Report (By the International Association of Chiefs of Police)
         1963-1965, Student Affairs, 1974-1979, and the White Burkett
         Miller Council -Correspondence 1976 Sept-1979 Dec.</p>
    </scopecontent>
